-------------------------- ACTIVE COMBAT BLOCK ---------------------
WEAPON: SAVALETTE GUARDIAN (Heavy Pistol)
- POOL: 15 (Pistols 6 + Spec 2 + AGI 5 + Smartlink 2)
- ACCURACY: 7 (Base 5 + Smartlink 2)
- DAMAGE: 8P | AP: -5 (APDS)
- MODES: SA / BF (Burst Fire)
=====================================================================

--------------------------- COMBAT FLOW ----------------------------
1. ATTACK: Skill Pool vs. Dodge
2. DV: Base 8P + Net Hits (Savalette)
3. AP: -1 (Base) + -4 (APDS) = -5 Total
4. SOAK: Target Body + (Armor - 5)

DAMAGE FLOW EXAMPLE:
1. Roll 17 dice vs Target Dodge.
2. If 3 net hits: Final DV = 11P (8 + 3).
3. Target Armor is reduced by 5.
4. Target Soaks with Body + Remaining Armor.

--------------------------- SITUATIONAL MODIFIERS ------------------
COMBAT:
- Target in good cover: +2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Target in full cover: +4 [SITUATIONAL]
- Called shot: -4 [SITUATIONAL]
- Running: -2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Recoil: -1 per shot after first [SITUATIONAL]
- Low-light conditions: +2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Target behind partial cover: -2 [SITUATIONAL]

SOCIAL:
- Negotiating from weakness: -2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Intimidation with leverage/physical threat: +2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Con vs. suspicious target: -2 to -4 [SITUATIONAL]
- First Impression: Already included (+2) [FIRST ENCOUNTER ONLY]
- Impersonating known person: +2 [SITUATIONAL: Social Chameleon]

STEALTH (Sneaking):
- Observers alert: -2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Moving at half speed: +2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Chameleon Suit active: +2 [SITUATIONAL: CAMO ACTIVE]

PERCEPTION:
- Distracted: -2 [SITUATIONAL]
- Using Earbuds 2: +2 audio [SITUATIONAL]
- Using Goggles 4: +4 visual [SITUATIONAL]
- Hawk Eye: Already included (+2 visual) [ALWAYS ACTIVE]

--------------------------- TAG GLOSSARY ---------------------------
[FOR LLM USE - Apply these rules when interpreting dice pools]

[ALWAYS ACTIVE] → Apply this modifier to every relevant roll without asking
[SITUATIONAL] → Ask player: "Does [condition] apply here?" before adding
[BASE] → The unmodified pool before situational modifiers
[UNTRAINED] → Roll uses attribute only; no skill ranks

[FIRST ENCOUNTER ONLY] → Only applies first time meeting an NPC
[WHEN HAGGLING] → Only applies during price negotiation
[WHEN USING PHYSICAL LEVERAGE] → Only applies when player has explicit physical advantage
[WHEN IMPERSONATING KNOWN PERSON] → Only applies when pretending to be someone specific
[WHEN IN URBAN ENVIRONMENT] → Only applies in city/industrial zones
[WHEN USING HEAVY PISTOL] → Only applies when wielding heavy pistol class weapon
[WHEN PICKING ELECTRONIC LOCKS] → Only applies to electronic lock picking tests
[WHEN USING TOOL KIT] → Only applies when hardware tool kit is available
[WHEN USING AUTOPICKER] → Only applies when autopicker device is available
[WHEN DECRYPTING] → Only applies to computer tests vs. encryption
[WHEN USING AUDIO ENHANCEMENTS] → Only applies when earbuds are active
[CAMO ACTIVE] → Only applies when Chameleon Suit is active and environment appropriate
[VISUAL ONLY] → Only applies to visual perception tests
